README
======

The USAS tools gem is designed to provide utilities for working with data formats used by the USAS semantic analysis system.

At the time of writing, this includes the ability to parse and validate semantic tags and full lexicons.

Build
-----

    $ gem build usastools.gemspec

Install
-------

    $ gem install usastools-x.x.x.gem
 

Use
---

See test.rb for a quick demo.  Basically, import `usastools/{semtag,lexicon}` to use the parsing features.
